<!-- FAQ Section -->
<section class="py-5">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title text-center">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <p class="text-center text-muted mb-5">Everything you need to know about our AI Portfolio Creator</p>

        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-lg-8">
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-header" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq1">
                        How does the AI select which projects to include?
                    </div>
                    <div id="faq1" class="collapse show faq-body">
                        <p>Our AI evaluates multiple factors including project complexity, relevance to your target jobs, demonstrated skills, results achieved, and visual appeal (for creative fields). It compares your work against successful portfolios in your industry to determine which projects will make the strongest impression.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-header collapsed" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq2">
                        Can I customize the AI-generated portfolio?
                    </div>
                    <div id="faq2" class="collapse faq-body">
                        <p>Absolutely! While the AI provides an excellent starting point, you have full control to edit any content, rearrange projects, change layouts, and customize colors/fonts. Many users start with the AI's suggestions and then add personal touches.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-header collapsed" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq3">
                        What types of work can I include in my portfolio?
                    </div>
                    <div id="faq3" class="collapse faq-body">
                        <p>Our AI portfolio builder supports all types of work: design files, code repositories, writing samples, marketing campaigns, business projects, photography, and more. You can upload files directly or connect to platforms like GitHub, Behance, or Google Drive.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-header collapsed" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq4">
                        Is there a limit to how many projects I can include?
                    </div>
                    <div id="faq4" class="collapse faq-body">
                        <p>The free plan allows up to 5 projects. Premium plans allow unlimited projects, and our AI will help you select the optimal number (typically 6-12) to showcase your range without overwhelming viewers.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-header collapsed" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq5">
                        How often does the AI update my portfolio?
                    </div>
                    <div id="faq5" class="collapse faq-body">
                        <p>Our AI continuously monitors your connected accounts (like GitHub or Behance) for new work. It will notify you when it finds new projects worth adding and suggest updates to keep your portfolio fresh. You control when changes are published.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

